data.description: Right in the heart of the action. This townhouse is located close to Elm Creek and Earl Brown parks with lost of shopping close by. Quick access to Hwy 10. This is a well maintained property with vaulted a ceiling in the living room with a fireplace. 2 large bedrooms with a full bath and loft in the upper level. Comes with a 2 car garage on a corner lot. The seller will replace the carpeting before closing in a neutral color.
